The Scroll-Space Timeline View gets a **third dimension toggle**.

**Default View (Linearized):** Shows one canonical path (configurable: `latest`, `first`, `user_selected`).

**Branch Explorer Mode:** Activates a **graph visualization overlay** on the timeline:

*   **Regeneration Nodes** appear as stacked cards at the same vertical position

*   **Edit History** appears as a clock icon; clicking shows version diff slider

